  {
    "row": 54,
    "rowsha": "VzDxHMl0vKby6BK5RJlfHxPFit1vMlpPiL5Nfi50CNE=",
    "originContent": "## ✨ Features",
    "translatedContent": "## ✨ Functionaliteiten"
  },
  {
    "row": 55,
    "rowsha": "xiu4mtNL2BpG/MeSdNpVNmn4h3XvIJqN4SkI2wkJ3as=",
    "originContent": "- [x] multiple out-of-the-box controls (buttons, labels, text boxes, check boxes, radio buttons, list views, tree views, combo boxes, date/time pickers, color pickers, tabs, accordions, etc.). A full list of controls can be found [here](https://gdt050579.github.io/AppCUI-rs/chapter-3/stock_controls.html) ",
    "translatedContent": "- [x] meerdere kant-en-klare besturingselementen (knoppen, labels, tekstvakken, selectievakjes, keuzerondjes, lijstweergaven, boomstructuren, comboboxen, datum/tijd-kiezers, kleurkiezers, tabbladen, accordeons, enz.). Een volledige lijst van besturingselementen is te vinden [hier](https://gdt050579.github.io/AppCUI-rs/chapter-3/stock_controls.html) "
  },
  {
    "row": 56,
    "rowsha": "T59OdCbjodbCRlT/6nYUj0SI7h/yufSPLFfkpp+BvqM=",
    "originContent": "- [x] powerful layout system that allows you to position controls using absolute coordinates, relative coordinates, docking, alignment, anchors, or pivot positioning (see more [here](https://gdt050579.github.io/AppCUI-rs/chapter-3/layout.html)) ",
    "translatedContent": "- [x] krachtig layout-systeem waarmee je besturingselementen kunt positioneren met absolute coördinaten, relatieve coördinaten, docking, uitlijning, ankers of pivot-positionering (zie meer [hier](https://gdt050579.github.io/AppCUI-rs/chapter-3/layout.html)) "
  },
  {
    "row": 57,
    "rowsha": "ctlQaQD1eSIdCe9+IaDMdbCx4gdBgXLaih2SjiVfo7I=",
    "originContent": "- [x] menus and toolbars",
    "translatedContent": "- [x] menu’s en werkbalken"
  },
  {
    "row": 58,
    "rowsha": "0Xr/slySqLUIxKC+TkJ8puizyj0oU8bX30a7TXC/MdM=",
    "originContent": "- [x] multi-platform support (Windows via API and virtual terminal, Linux via ncurses, macOS via termios)",
    "translatedContent": "- [x] multi-platform ondersteuning (Windows via API en virtueel terminal, Linux via ncurses, macOS via termios)"
  },
  {
    "row": 59,
    "rowsha": "viMQycVhnxGtszgm7wJxAXKLBavEFYkmXaJt8dfjykM=",
    "originContent": "- [x] multi-threading support to allow background tasks",
    "translatedContent": "- [x] multi-threading ondersteuning voor achtergrondtaken"
  },
  {
    "row": 60,
    "rowsha": "LaoHA+rbSuVhmpRVwrWZkhX3ldJzxI3LQap9KCdC3/w=",
    "originContent": "- [x] timers",
    "translatedContent": "- [x] timers"
  },
  {
    "row": 61,
    "rowsha": "I3o96a39Z4kn8KJeikDQDOMS6LKPTbePdV9wiIDyVsU=",
    "originContent": "- [x] mouse support",
    "translatedContent": "- [x] muisondersteuning"
